FallbackEndpointTooltip=Only used when no server resolves at all (neither this row nor the module default has one). Not part of the real PrintBridge Server API - it's a plain URL with no auth, for simple test receivers like the bundled one. If you've set up a server and token above, leave this blank; it will never be used.
