ProfileParameterInstructions=To use a profile from TakePOS, create or edit a printer in Setup > Receipt Printers with connector type "Local Printer" and paste the pridge://<id> value shown above into its Parameter field.
PridgeProfilesHelp=Adopting a printer above already creates its profile automatically - you only see a printer to pick here if it's already wired to pridge:// (via Adopt or by hand) but has no profile yet, e.g. after a database reset. Never type a ref by hand: the picker only ever lists what a printer's Parameter already holds, so it can't drift out of sync.
NoAdoptedPrinterWithoutProfile=No adopted printer is missing a profile right now - adopt one above first, or every adopted printer already has a profile below.
