AdoptExistingPrinters=Adopt an existing printer (Local Printers)
AdoptExistingPrintersHelp=Only printers using the built-in module's "Local Printer" connector type can be adopted: Dummy has nothing to intercept, and Network/Local Windows Printer/Cups printers never go through a mechanism Pridge can hook into. Adopting a printer overwrites its current Parameter value.
NoFileTypePrinterFound=No "Local Printer" type printer found in the built-in Receipt Printers module.
